    63→# New features
    65→## chainable methods
    67→TS-Pattern v5's major addition is the ability to chain methods to narrow down the values matched by primitive patterns, like `P.string` or `P.number`.
    68→
    69→Since a few examples is worth a thousand words, here are a few ways you can use chainable methods:
